ments":"{\"subtask_idx\": 0, \"state\": \"in_progress\"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Subtask at index 0, named '检查报表文件是否存在' is marked as 'in_progress' successfully.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_mwES7hoJQoTUMlBrqXa2nn00"},{"role":"assistant","content":"现在执行第一个子任务，检查报表文件是否存在。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_OccvwDCY4YG0H16CbyWACVEb","type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_get_Report","arguments":"{}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"{\"exists\": true, \"message\": \"报表文件存在\"}","tool_call_id":"call_00_OccvwDCY4YG0H16CbyWACVEb"},{"role":"user","content":"<system-hint>The current plan:\n```\n# 全行报表查询与核对\n**Description**: 执行全行报表的查询流程：首先检查报表文件是否存在，然后核对报表中明细金额列的合计是否等于最后一行合计金额，最后获取报表内容并展示给用户。确保报表数据的完整性和准确性。\n**Expected Outcome**: 完成报表查询流程，返回报表存在性检查结果、金额核对结果以及完整的报表内容供前端展示\n**State**: todo\n**Created At**: 2026-04-12 12:34:15\n## Subtasks\n- [ ] [WIP] 检查报表文件是否存在\n- [ ] 核对报表金额合计\n- [ ] 获取并展示报表内容\n\n```\nNow the subtask at index 0, named '检查报表文件是否存在', is 'in_progress'. Its details are as follows:\n```\n- [ ] [WIP] 检查报表文件是否存在\n\t- Created At: 2026-04-12 12:28:42\n\t- Description: 调用Tool_get_Report工具检查full_report.csv文件是否存在\n\t- Expected Outcome: 返回报表文件的存在性检查结果\n\t- State: in_progress\n```\nYour options include:\n- Go on execute the subtask and get the outcome.\n- Call 'finish_subtask' with the specific outcome if the subtask is finished.\n- Ask the user for more information if you need.\n- Revise the plan by calling 'revise_current_plan' if necessary.\n- If the user asks you to do something unrelated to the plan, prioritize the completion of user's query first, and then return to the plan afterward.\nImportant Rules: \n- Update before processing each subtask: When processing each subtask, call get_subtask_count and view_subtasks to confirm the latest information: get_subtask_count is used to confirm the total number of subtasks to avoid omissions;view_subtasks is used to query subtask information, execute subtasks strictly according to the latest information, and pay attention to ignoring the original request.\n- User May Modify Plan: Users can directly add, edit, or delete subtasks without going through you.\n- Only focus on the current content: Always follow the latest plan content, especially when the original plan conflicts with the latest queried plan, follow the latest queried plan without considering the initial requirements.\n- Do not modify plan: Do not modify or amend the plan without a clear plan modification instruction from user\n- Language consistency: Respond to users in the same language as the plan\n</system-hint>","name":"user01"}],"stream":false,"tools":[{"type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_plan","description":"Finish the current plan by given outcome, or abandon it","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"state":{"type":"string","description":"The state to finish the plan: done/abandoned"},"outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The specific outcome of the plan if done, or reason if abandoned"}},"required":["state","outcome"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_chk_Report","description":"核对报表中明细金额列的合计是否等于最后一行合计金额","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"update_subtask_state","description":"Update the state of a subtask by given index and state","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"integer","description":"The index of the subtask to be updated, starting from 0"},"state":{"type":"string","description":"The new state: todo/in_progress/abandoned"}},"required":["subtask_idx","state"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"view_subtasks","description":"View the details of the sub-tasks by given indexes","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"integer"},"description":"The indexes of the sub-tasks to be viewed, starting from 0"}},"required":["subtask_idx"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"view_historical_plans","description":"View the historical plans","parameters