"planName\": \"计划名称\",\r\n  \"plan_context\": \"返回给用户的计划方案描述\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n- `NEED_MORE`: 计划已生成，提示用户确认或修改\r\n- `CONFIRMED`: 计划已确认，可以执行\r\n\n\n用户输入: 报表查询","name":"user01"},{"role":"assistant","content":"用户输入\"报表查询\"，这明确表示要执行报表查询。根据系统规则，当用户请求已经暗示执行意图时，我应该直接开始执行计划。\n\n让我创建一个新的报表查询计划。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_SGL74tyLOAI9rghhZdwRCDsk","type":"function","function":{"name":"create_plan","arguments":"{\"name\": \"全行报表查询与核对\", \"description\": \"执行全行报表的查询流程：首先检查报表文件是否存在，然后核对报表中明细金额列的合计是否等于最后一行合计金额，最后获取报表内容并展示给用户。确保报表数据的完整性和准确性。\", \"expected_outcome\": \"完成报表查询流程，返回报表存在性检查结果、金额核对结果以及完整的报表内容供前端展示\", \"subtasks\": [{\"name\":\"检查报表文件是否存在\",\"description\":\"调用Tool_get_Report工具检查full_report.csv文件是否存在\",\"expected_outcome\":\"返回报表文件的存在性检查结果\"},{\"name\":\"核对报表金额合计\",\"description\":\"调用Tool_chk_Report工具核对报表中明细金额列的合计是否等于最后一行合计金额\",\"expected_outcome\":\"返回金额核对结果，确认数据一致性\"},{\"name\":\"获取并展示报表内容\",\"description\":\"调用Tool_dis_Report工具获取报表内容，供Agent推送到前端展示\",\"expected_outcome\":\"返回完整的报表内容\"}]}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Plan '全行报表查询与核对' created successfully.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_SGL74tyLOAI9rghhZdwRCDsk"},{"role":"assistant","content":"用户输入\"报表查询\"，这明确表示要执行报表查询。根据系统规则，当用户请求已经暗示执行意图时，我应该直接开始执行计划。\n\n让我先查看当前计划的状态。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_EbaylC7EfpEkSYOhnfinBdYp","type":"function","function":{"name":"get_subtask_count","arguments":"{}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Current plan '全行报表查询与核对' has 3 subtask(s): 0 done, 0 in_progress, 3 todo, 0 abandoned.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_EbaylC7EfpEkSYOhnfinBdYp"},{"role":"assistant","content":"用户输入\"报表查询\"，这明确表示要执行报表查询。根据系统规则，当用户请求已经暗示执行意图时，我应该直接开始执行计划。\n\n让我开始执行第一个子任务：检查报表文件是否存在。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_7XD1OlZJIiQ6xideC5yUqnON","type":"function","function":{"name":"update_subtask_state","arguments":"{\"subtask_idx\": 0, \"state\": \"in_progress\"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Subtask at index 0, named '检查报表文件是否存在' is marked as 'in_progress' successfully.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_7XD1OlZJIiQ6xideC5yUqnON"},{"role":"user","content":"<system-hint>The current plan:\n```\n# 全行报表查询与核对\n**Description**: 执行全行报表的查询流程：首先检查报表文件是否存在，然后核对报表中明细金额列的合计是否等于最后一行合计金额，最后获取报表内容并展示给用户。确保报表数据的完整性和准确性。\n**Expected Outcome**: 完成报表查询流程，返回报表存在性检查结果、金额核对结果以及完整的报表内容供前端展示\n**State**: todo\n**Created At**: 2026-04-12 12:53:46\n## Subtasks\n- [ ] [WIP] 检查报表文件是否存在\n- [ ] 核对报表金额合计\n- [ ] 获取并展示报表内容\n\n```\nNow the subtask at index 0, named '检查报表文件是否存在', is 'in_progress'. Its details are as follows:\n```\n- [ ] [WIP] 检查报表文件是否存在\n\t- Created At: 2026-04-12 12:53:46\n\t- Description: 调用Tool_get_Report工具检查full_report.csv文件是否存在\n\t- Expected Outcome: 返回报表文件的存在性检查结果\n\t- State: in_progress\n```\nYour options include:\n- Go on execute the subtask and get the outcome.\n- Call 'finish_subtask' with the specific outcome if the subtask is finished.\n- Ask the user for more information if you need.\n- Revise the plan by calling 'revise_current_plan' if necessary.\n- If the user asks you to do something unrelated to the plan, prioritize the completion of user's query first, and then return to the plan afterward.\nImportant Rules: \n- Update before processing each subtask: When processing each subtask, call get_subtask_count and view_subtasks to confirm the latest information: get_subtask_count is used to confirm the total number of subtasks to avoid omissions;view_subtasks is used to query subtask information, execute subtasks strictly according to the latest information, and pay attention to ignoring the original request.\n- User May Modify Plan: Users can directly add, edit, or delete subtasks without going through you.\n- Only focus on the current content: Always follow the latest plan content, especially when the original plan conflicts with the latest queried plan, follow the latest queried plan without considering the initial requirements.\n- Do not modify plan: Do not modify or amend the plan without a clear plan modification instruction from user\n- Language consistency: Respond to users in the same language as the plan\n</system-hint>","name":"user01"}],"stream":false,"tools":[{"type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_plan","description":"Finish the current plan by given outcome, or abandon it","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"state":{"type":"string","description":"The state to finish the plan: done/abandoned"},"outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The specific outcome of the plan if done, or reason if abandoned"}},"required":["state","outcome"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_chk_Report","description":"核对报表中明细金额列的合计是否等于最后一行合计金额","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"update_subtask_state","description":"Update the state of a subtask by given index and state","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"integer","description":"The index of the subtask to be updated, starting from 0"},"state":{"type":"string","description":"The new state: todo/in_progress/abandoned"}},"required":["subtask_idx","state"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"view_subtasks","description":"View the details of the sub-tasks by given indexes","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"integer"},"description":"The indexes of the sub-tasks to be viewed, starting from 0"}},"required":["subtask_idx"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"view_historical_plans","description":"View the historical plans","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"recover_historical_plan","description":"Recover a historical plan by given plan ID","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"plan_id":{"type":"string","description":"The ID of the historical plan to be recovered"}},"required":["plan_id"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"revise_current_plan","description":"Revise the current plan by adding, revising or deleting a sub-task","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"integer","description":"The index of the sub-task to be revised, starting from 0"},"action":{"type":"string","description":"The action to be performed: add/revise/delete"},"subtask":{"type":"object","description":"The sub-task to be added or revised (required for add/revise)"}},"required":["subtask_idx","action","subtask"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"create_plan","description":"Create a plan by given name and sub-tasks","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtasks":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"object"},"description":"A list of sequential sub-tasks. Each subtask must be an object with: 'name' (string, required), 'description' (string), 'expected_outcome' (string). Example: [{\"name\": \"Calculate area\", \"description\": \"Multiply length by width\", \"expected_outcome\": \"Area value\"}]"},"name":{"type":"string","description":"The plan name, should be concise, descriptive and not exceed 10 words"},"description":{"type":"string","description":"The plan description, including the constraints, target and outcome to be achieved. The description should be clear, specific and concise, and all the constraints, target and outcome should be specific and measurable"},"expected_outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The expected outcome of the plan, which should be specific, concrete and measurable"}},"required":["name","description","expected_outcome","subtasks"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_subtask","description":"Label the subtask as done by given index and outcome","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"integer","description":"The index of the sub-task to be marked as done, starting from 0"},"subtask_outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The specific outcome of the sub-task, should exactly match the expected outcome in the sub-task description. SHOULDN'T be what you did or general description, e.g. \"I have searched xxx\", \"I have written the code for xxx\", etc. It SHOULD be the specific data, information, or path to the file, e.g. \"There are 5 articles about xxx, they are\\n- xxx\\n- xxx\\n...\""}},"required":["subtask_idx","subtask_outcome"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_dis_Report","description":"获取报表内容，返回给 Agent 推送到前端展示","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"load_skill_through_path","description":"Load and activate a skill resource by its ID and resource path.\n\n**Functionality:**\n1. Activates the specified skill (making its tools available)\n2. Returns the requested resource content\n usage instructions)\n- 'SKILL.md': The skill's markdown documentation (name, description,- Other paths: Additional resources like scripts, configs, templates, or data files","parameters":{"type":"object","required":["skillId","path"],"properties":{"skillId":{"type":"string","description":"The unique identifier of the skill.","enum":["plando_report_wj_custom"]},"path":{"description":"The path to the resource file within the skill (e.g., 'SKILL.md, references/references.md')","type":"string"}}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"update_plan_info","description":"Update the current plan's name, description, or expected outcome. Pass null or empty string to keep a field unchanged.","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"name":{"type":"string","description":"The new plan name (optional, pass null or empty to keep unchanged)"},"description":{"type":"string","description":"The new plan description (optional, pass null or empty to keep unchanged)"},"expected_outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The new expected outcome (optional, pass null or empty to keep unchanged)"}},"required":["name","description","expected_outcome"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_get_Report","description":"检查 full_report.csv 是否存在，返回存在性结果","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"get_subtask_count","description":"Get the number of subtasks in the c