ask at index 2, named '获取并展示报表内容', is 'in_progress'. Its details are as follows:\n```\n- [ ] [WIP] 获取并展示报表内容\n\t- Created At: 2026-04-12 12:53:46\n\t- Description: 调用Tool_dis_Report工具获取报表内容，供Agent推送到前端展示\n\t- Expected Outcome: 返回完整的报表内容\n\t- State: in_progress\n```\nYour options include:\n- Go on execute the subtask and get the outcome.\n- Call 'finish_subtask' with the specific outcome if the subtask is finished.\n- Ask the user for more information if you need.\n- Revise the plan by calling 'revise_current_plan' if necessary.\n- If the user asks you to do something unrelated to the plan, prioritize the completion of user's query first, and then return to the plan afterward.\nImportant Rules: \n- Update before processing each subtask: When processing each subtask, call get_subtask_count and view_subtasks to confirm the latest information: get_subtask_count is used to confirm the total number of subtasks to avoid omissions;view_subtasks is used to query subtask information, execute subtasks strictly according to the latest information, and pay attention to ignoring the original request.\n- User May Modify Plan: Users can directly add, edit, or delete subtasks without going through you.\n- Only focus on the current content: Always follow the latest plan content, especially when the original plan conflicts with the latest queried plan, follow the latest queried plan without considering the initial requirements.\n- Do not modify plan: Do not modify or amend the plan without a clear plan modification instruction from user\n- Language consistency: Respond to users in the same language as the plan\n</system-hint>","name":"user01"}],"stream":false,"tools":[{"type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_plan","description":"Finish the current plan by given outcome, or abandon it","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"state":{"type":"string","description":"The state to finish the plan: done/abandoned"},"outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The specific outcome of the plan if done, or reason if abandoned"}},"required":["state","outcome"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_chk_Report","description":"核对报表中明细金额列的合计是否等于最后一行合计金额","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"update_subtask_state","description":"Update the state of a subtask by given index and state","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"integer","description":"The index of the subtask to be updated, starting from 0"},"state":{"type":"string","description":"The new state: todo/in_progress/abandoned"}},"required":["subtask_idx","state"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"view_subtasks","description":"View the details of the sub-tasks by given indexes","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"integer"},"description":"The indexes of the sub-tasks to be viewed, starting from 0"}},"required":["subtask_idx"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"view_historical_plans","description":"View the historical plans","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"recover_historical_plan","description":"Recover a historical plan by given plan ID","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"plan_id":{"type":"string","description":"The ID of the historical plan to be recovered"}},"required":["plan_id"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"revise_current_plan","description":"Revise the current plan by adding, revising or deleting a sub-task","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"integer","description":"The index of the sub-task to be revised, starting from 0"},"action":{"type":"string","description":"The action to be performed: add/revise/delete"},"subtask":{"type":"object","description":"The sub-task to be added or revised (required for add/revise)"}},"required":["subtask_idx","action","subtask"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"create_plan","description":"Create a plan by given name and sub-tasks","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtasks":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"object"},"description":"A list of sequential sub-tasks. Each subtask must be an object with: 'name' (string, required), 'description' (string), 'expected_outcome' (string). Example: [{\"name\": \"Calculate area\", \"description\": \"Multiply length by width\", \"expected_outcome\": \"Area value\"}]"},"name":{"type":"string","description":"The plan name, should be concise, descriptive and not exceed 10 words"},"description":{"type":"string","description":"The plan description, including the constraints, target and outcome to be achieved. The description should be clear, specific and concise, and all the constraints, target and outcome should be specific and measurable"},"expected_outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The expected outcome of the plan, which should be specific, concrete and measurable"}},"required":["name","description","expected_outcome","subtasks"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_subtask","description":"Label the subtask as done by given index and outcome","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"integer","description":"The index of the sub-task to be marked as done, starting from 0"},"subtask_outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The specific outcome of the sub-task, should exactly match the expected outcome in the sub-task description. SHOULDN'T be what you did or general description, e.g. \"I have searched xxx\", \"I have written the code for xxx\", etc. It SHOULD be the specific data, information, or path to the file, e.g. \"There are 5 articles about xxx, they are\\n- xxx\\n- xxx\\n...\""}},"required":["subtask_idx","subtask_outcome"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_dis_Report","description":"获取报表内容，返回给 Agent 推送到前端展示","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"load_skill_through_path","description":"Load and ac