d), 'description' (string), 'expected_outcome' (string). Example: [{\"name\": \"Calculate area\", \"description\": \"Multiply length by width\", \"expected_outcome\": \"Area value\"}]"},"name":{"type":"string","description":"The plan name, should be concise, descriptive and not exceed 10 words"},"description":{"type":"string","description":"The plan description, including the constraints, target and outcome to be achieved. The description should be clear, specific and concise, and all the constraints, target and outcome should be specific and measurable"},"expected_outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The expected outcome of the plan, which should be specific, concrete and measurable"}},"required":["name","description","expected_outcome","subtasks"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_subtask","description":"Label the subtask as done by given index and outcome","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"subtask_idx":{"type":"integer","description":"The index of the sub-task to be marked as done, starting from 0"},"subtask_outcome":{"type":"string","description":"The specific outcome of the sub-task, should exactly match the expected outcome in the sub-task description. SHOULDN'T be what you did or general description, e.g. \"I have searched xxx\", \"I have written the code for xxx\", etc. It SHOULD be the specific data, information, or path to the file, e.g. \"There are 5 articles about xxx, they are\\n- xxx\\n- xxx\\n...\""}},"required":["subtask_idx","subtask_outcome"]}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_dis_Report","description":"获取报表内容，返回给 Agent 推送到前端展示","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{}}}},{"type":"function","function":{"name":"load_skill_through_path","description":"Load and activate a skill resource by its ID and resource path.\n\n**Functionality:**\n1. Activates the specified skill (making its tools available)\n2. Returns the requested resource content\n usage instructions)\n- 'SKILL.md': The skill's markdown documen