uments":"{\"subtask_idx\": 0, \"state\": \"in_progress\"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Subtask at index 0, named '检查报表文件是否存在' is marked as 'in_progress' successfully.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_mwES7hoJQoTUMlBrqXa2nn00"},{"role":"assistant","content":"现在执行第一个子任务，检查报表文件是否存在。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_OccvwDCY4YG0H16CbyWACVEb","type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_get_Report","arguments":"{}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"{\"exists\": true, \"message\": \"报表文件存在\"}","tool_call_id":"call_00_OccvwDCY4YG0H16CbyWACVEb"},{"role":"assistant","content":"第一个子任务已完成，现在标记为完成。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_T4Klqgnl15xsl3iikWq3wwcJ","type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_subtask","arguments":"{\"subtask_idx\": 0, \"subtask_outcome\": \"报表文件存在\"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Subtask (at index 0) named '检查报表文件是否存在' is marked as done successfully. The next subtask (at index 1) named '核对报表金额合计' is activated.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_T4Klqgnl15xsl3iikWq3wwcJ"},{"role":"assistant","content":"现在执行第二个子任务：核对报表金额合计。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_8PemImCWwtbP6j358wpQdfNw","type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_chk_Report","arguments":"{}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"Error: 报表缺少必要的列，需要包含'明细金额'和'合计金额'列","tool_call_id":"call_00_8PemImCWwtbP6j358wpQdfNw"},{"role":"assistant","content":"第二个子任务执行时遇到了错误：报表缺少必要的列，需要包含'明细金额'和'合计金额'列。这个错误表明报表结构不符合预期，无法完成金额核对。\n\n让我先标记这个子任务为完成，并记录错误结果。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_FoiPYd4SXYqbk7S5EFHw4Di5","type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_subtask","arguments":"{\"subtask_idx\": 1, \"subtask_outcome\": \"报表缺少必要的列，需要包含'明细金额'和'合计金额'列，无法完成金额核对\"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Subtask (at index 1) named '核对报表金额合计' is marked as done successfully. The next subtask (at index 2) named '获取并展示报表内容' is activated.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_FoiPYd4SXYqbk7S5EFHw4Di5"},{"role":"assistant","content":"现在执行第三个子任务：获取并展示报表内容。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_r8Hf6YqUyVZzTMFf35w9ikRe","type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_dis_Report","argume