询与核对' created successfully.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_SGL74tyLOAI9rghhZdwRCDsk"},{"role":"assistant","content":"用户输入\"报表查询\"，这明确表示要执行报表查询。根据系统规则，当用户请求已经暗示执行意图时，我应该直接开始执行计划。\n\n让我先查看当前计划的状态。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_EbaylC7EfpEkSYOhnfinBdYp","type":"function","function":{"name":"get_subtask_count","arguments":"{}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Current plan '全行报表查询与核对' has 3 subtask(s): 0 done, 0 in_progress, 3 todo, 0 abandoned.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_EbaylC7EfpEkSYOhnfinBdYp"},{"role":"assistant","content":"用户输入\"报表查询\"，这明确表示要执行报表查询。根据系统规则，当用户请求已经暗示执行意图时，我应该直接开始执行计划。\n\n让我开始执行第一个子任务：检查报表文件是否存在。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_7XD1OlZJIiQ6xideC5yUqnON","type":"function","function":{"name":"update_subtask_state","arguments":"{\"subtask_idx\": 0, \"state\": \"in_progress\"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Subtask at index 0, named '检查报表文件是否存在' is marked as 'in_progress' successfully.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_7XD1OlZJIiQ6xideC5yUqnON"},{"role":"assistant","content":"现在执行第一个子任务：检查报表文件是否存在。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_GeE3S2tws36xLaNPZlhsUjqk","type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_get_Report","arguments":"{}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"{\"exists\": true, \"message\": \"报表文件存在\"}","tool_call_id":"call_00_GeE3S2tws36xLaNPZlhsUjqk"},{"role":"assistant","content":"第一个子任务已完成，现在标记为完成。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_aac5I9RDRBr4E8pMvBbueEos","type":"function","function":{"name":"finish_subtask","arguments":"{\"subtask_idx\": 0, \"subtask_outcome\": \"报表文件存在\"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"\"Subtask (at index 0) named '检查报表文件是否存在' is marked as done successfully. The next subtask (at index 1) named '核对报表金额合计' is activated.\"","tool_call_id":"call_00_aac5I9RDRBr4E8pMvBbueEos"},{"role":"assistant","content":"现在执行第二个子任务：核对报表金额合计。","tool_calls":[{"id":"call_00_GRQyTkJ2WsPPjtV2M4hBOjOh","type":"function","function":{"name":"Tool_chk_Report","arguments":"{}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"Error: 报表缺少必要的列，需要包含'明细金额'和'合计金额'列","tool_call_id":"call_00_GRQyTkJ2WsPPjtV2